1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
One harvests chemical energy; the other harvests light.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:07,200
Both processes are vital for life on Earth and beyond.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:11,200
Photosynthesis converts sunlight into energy, fueling plants and, ultimately, animals.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:16,400
On the flip side, chemosynthesis thrives in dark, extreme environments, like deep-sea vents.

5
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:20,800
Both processes create ecosystems, proving life can adapt in unimaginable ways.

6
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:24,400
Want to learn more about the science behind life?

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,200
Hit subscribe!
